    "body": "Now that we have pre-commit config in place #2403 we can think about some standardization. \r\n \r\nhttps://github.com/pre-commit/pre-commit-hooks contains a number of useful pre-commit hooks that can help this repo enforce standardization across different tools and developers. Such\r\n- [Trailing white space fixer](https://github.com/pre-commit/pre-commit-hooks/blob/master/pre_commit_hooks/trailing_whitespace_fixer.py) \r\n- [Inconsistent line breaks](https://github.com/pre-commit/pre-commit-hooks/blob/master/pre_commit_hooks/mixed_line_ending.py). E.g  some csv files use CRLF whereas all the rest just LF\r\n- [Large files check](https://github.com/pre-commit/pre-commit-hooks/blob/master/pre_commit_hooks/check_added_large_files.py) #2644 \r\n-  TBD ...",
